    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. I have babied this car from day one, and it is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it still feels brand new! It drives like a dream and looks even better. I'm looking for a quick, smooth sale, so I've priced it to move. Come take a look and see for yourself why I'm so excited about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
